OL,3,C'Brand Beckham': How damaging are
OL,4,CBrooklyn's bombshell claims?
OL,6,FRumours of a rift in the Beckham
OL,7,Ffamily had been circulating in the
OL,8,Fmedia for some time, with family
OL,9,Fmembers reportedly blocking each other
OL,10,Fon social media, and Brooklyn failing
OL,11,Fto attend his father's 50th birthday
OL,12,Fparty.
OL,14,FThe lengthy post, and first direct
OL,15,Fpublic acknowledgement of the feud,
OL,16,Fhas led some to question what the long-
OL,17,Fterm implications could be for a
OL,18,Ffamily that prides itself on the
OL,19,Ftightly controlled "Beckham brand".
