OL,3,C'Brand Beckham': How damaging are
OL,4,CBrooklyn's bombshell claims?
OL,6,FSir David Beckham and Victoria married
OL,7,Fin 1999, while David was a successful
OL,8,Ffootballer and Victoria was known for
OL,9,Fher musical career in the Spice Girls.
OL,11,FWith so many years spent in the public
OL,12,Feye, both individually and as a
OL,13,Fcouple, many in the public viewed them
OL,14,Fas a relatable family.
OL,16,FRecent fly-on-the-wall documentaries,
OL,17,Fwhich the Beckhams remained executive
OL,18,Fproducers on, gave people a look
OL,19,Fbehind closed doors and only served to
OL,20,Fdeepen the relationship people felt to
OL,21,Fthe pair.
