OL,3,C'Brand Beckham': How damaging are
OL,4,CBrooklyn's bombshell claims?
OL,6,FBrand and Culture Expert Nick Ede told
OL,7,FITV News the Beckhams had, for many,
OL,8,F"always represented aspiration, hard
OL,9,Fwork and family."
OL,11,FHe went on to add that: "For many
OL,12,Fpeople, the Beckhams symbolise a
OL,13,Fmodern British family that grew up in
OL,14,Fpublic but tried to stay grounded.
OL,16,F"That emotional connection is a huge
OL,17,Fpart of why the brand has endured and
OL,18,Fwhy they have made so much money and
OL,19,Fare even more famous today than ever."
OL,21,FHow could the feud damage the Beckhams?
