OL,4,CBrooklyn's bombshell claims?
OL,6,FBrooklyn claimed in his Instagram post
OL,7,Fthat he "had been silent for years",
OL,8,Fbut had decided to speak out after his
OL,9,Fparents "continued to go to the press,
OL,10,Fleaving me with no choice but to speak
OL,11,Ffor myself and tell the truth".
OL,13,FHe said: "I do not want to reconcile
OL,14,Fwith my family. I'm not being
OL,15,Fcontrolled, I'm standing up for myself
OL,16,Ffor the first time in my life. For my
OL,17,Fentire life, my parents have
OL,18,Fcontrolled narratives in the press
OL,19,Fabout our family.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
