OL,6,FNick Ede told ITV News that while the
OL,7,Fimmediate conclusion could be that
OL,8,Fpeople will begin to see the cracks in
OL,9,Fan outwardly perfect public persona,
OL,10,Fin the long-term, the feud may
OL,11,Factually serve to strengthen people's
OL,12,Faffinity for the family.
OL,14,F"From a brand point of view, empathy
OL,15,Factually matters more than perfection
OL,16,Fnow," he said.
