OL,6,FWhilst Brooklyn said he is not
OL,7,Finterested in reconciling with his
OL,8,Fparents, we have yet to hear from
OL,9,FVictoria and David.
OL,11,FPaul said the language used by
OL,12,FBrooklyn gives some clues.
OL,14,F"The language used in the statement is
OL,15,Ffascinating from a reputation
OL,16,Fperspective," he said.
OL,18,F"By stating that he does not seek a
OL,19,Freconciliation with his parents, he
OL,20,Fhas effectively closed the door to a
OL,21,Fretaliatory media response from them.
