OL,6,F"This is important. Emotionally
OL,7,Fcharged statements levied at one party
OL,8,Fwill invariably be met with many
OL,9,Fequally high emotions by the other.
OL,10,FThe worst thing that the Beckhams
OL,11,Fcould do is issue a response
OL,12,Faddressing the allegations.
OL,14,F"Doing so simply risks a very public
OL,15,Fand potentially reputationally
OL,16,Fdamaging tit-for-tat, which never
OL,17,Flooks good and could escalate out of
OL,18,Fcontrol."
